
<section id="how">
  <span class="section-tag">How it works</span>
  <h2 class="section-h2 serif">Three steps.<br />Then we handle everything else.</h2>
  <p class="section-lead">From your first reply to a running ATM in your location — the process is designed to require as little from you as possible.</p>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num serif">01</span>
      <div class="step-icon">✉️</div>
      <div class="step-title">You reply to us</div>
      <div class="step-text">
        No meeting required. No forms to fill. Send us a message and we'll send you
        a copy of our 6-month trial agreement for review.
        Read it, ask questions, decide at your own pace.
      </div>
      <div class="step-time">No commitment at this stage</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num serif">02</span>
      <div class="step-icon">📋</div>
      <div class="step-title">We sign and schedule</div>
      <div class="step-text">
        Once you're comfortable, we sign the agreement and schedule installation.
        You provide your legal business name, a W-9, and ACH authorization for
        commission deposits. That's the full list of what we need from you.
      </div>
      <div class="step-time">15 – 20 business days to installation</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num serif">03</span>
      <div class="step-icon">💰</div>
      <div class="step-title">We install. You earn.</div>
      <div class="step-text">
        Our team installs the unit, anchors it, connects it, and verifies operations.
        From that point, we handle all cash loading, maintenance, repairs and
        24/7 monitoring. Your first commission arrives within 45 days of the
        first full operating month.
      </div>
      <div class="step-time">Monthly direct deposit via PAI — Brinks</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
